					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p221982">Re: Is NES/Famicom detection possible?</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=221982#p221982"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Wed Jul 25, 2018 6:11 am&nbsp;</div></td>
